channel.title: 3.2 Upload Model to S3 :: Deploy TensorFlow model on AWS with EC2 and Docker
channel.description: Create S3 Bucket Go to S3 Console: Click Bucket, then Create bucket. In the Create bucket tab: Bucket name: bucket-nlp-models-1 Leave the rest as default and click Create bucket. Upload Model to S3 In the bucket-nlp-models-1 bucket, click Upload. Click Add folder, navigate to the folder nmt on local machine then click Upload.
